"ID"=hex:33,02

[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Garmin\MapSource\Families\FAMILY_563\1]
"Bmap"="C:\\Garmin\\FAMILY_563\\basemap.img"
"Tdb"="C:\\Garmin\\FAMILY_563\\product.tdb"
"Loc"="C:\\Garmin\\FAMILY_563"
